Package: mixchisq
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for Mixtures of Chi-Square Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Julius", family = "Olaifa", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "julius.olaifa@okstate.edu"),
    person(given = "Pratyaydipta", family = "Rudra", role = c("aut"),
           email = "prudra@okstate.edu")
    )
Description: Provides utilities for finite mixtures of chi-square distributions,
    including density, distribution, quantile, and random generation functions.
    The package supports chi-bar-square style mixtures that include an atom at zero,
    which are useful as reference distributions in constrained likelihood ratio tests.
